Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}decided long ago in the past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed into a marriage\Nand left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Sanji learned\NPudding's terrible real character{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Big Mom's plot to seize Germa's scientific technology\Nby killing them all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything was a setup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your most recent memories \Ninvolving me have been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a joyous wedding tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A captured Luffy ignored Nami's pleas{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and continued to try to break free\Nat the expense of his own arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Thousand Brick...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you got caught.\NI'm glad that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, do you want to get out of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Sora's Wish!\NGerma's Failure - Sanji!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:02.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,MEDICAL CENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was bleeding badly\Nbut the wound already started healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has unbelievably hard skin\Nand strong recuperative power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how Germa's modified humans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she stays in bed, I think\Nshe'll heal enough to attend the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with her all night tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to notify the Vinsmokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the medical center\Non the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many wounded people\Nacross the castle tonight - I don't have time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your service. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt my leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember how that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was walking around the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into some soldiers who \Nwere going after intruders...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I got involved, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel right, does it?\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory has been overwritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell you what \Nreally happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break these bars already, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:13.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PRISON LIBRARY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:21.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Brick Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I expected of Montd'Or's book!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I gotta tear my arms apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Books can be destroyed by fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna burn the cage?\NAre you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you two can get out of there\Nbefore you're engulfed in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the only way to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know when you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright. Do it!\N--That quick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm still not ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really gonna burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's burning up there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to hear things too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want fire sparks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:08:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Luffy! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been through\Nsomething like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,\NI didn't have to rip my arms apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in some prison like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! They were all captured in the same book\Nas you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Books is as big as your imagination\Nwhich means it's infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:09:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom has so many strong lackeys\Nlike Montd'Or.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Jimbei!\NBut why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun Pirates that I led are also\Naffiliated with Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is a rebellion.\NI can't go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Fish-Man Island,\Nyou said that you had responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone heard screams \Nfrom the Prison Library!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's going on?!\N--They've already noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're indeed quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to hide\Nwhere they can't find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Let's go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got hungry all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get hungry under these circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy expends three times more energy\Nthan others doing even the simplest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm not saying \Nthat I wanna eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach is growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't eat anything \Nother than what you cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get hungry or \Nspears rain down on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay right here and wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Jimbei, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was proposed to by Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to marry him because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that idiot who played right into my hands\Nand fell for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be shot dead by my own hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the middle of the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't get any worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all fooled! Sanji, too!\NI gotta let him know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after Nami, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, wait!\NThere are tons of tough enemies in the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not fully recovered!\NDon't you remember what happened this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna be defeated this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I do.\NI know you wouldn't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't realize\NPudding's real character was this heinous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't completely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought she seemed a bit too perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was spying on her on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she wasn't planning to marry me from the \Nbeginning and they were gonna kill us all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the promise to pardon Luffy and the others\Nas long as I married her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't mean anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everything would be alright\Nif I sacrifice myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was just a fantasy!\NHow could I be so naive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father is a smart man\Nbut he was being too arrogant in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dealing with the Emperor.\NHe should've been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a good opportunity for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Germa should be allowed\Nto be brought down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pretend that we don't know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let Big Mom do as she has plotted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:13:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! If you attend the tea party,\Nyou're gonna die too, Reiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you worried for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parting memories are suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you're indebted to me\Nfor helping you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of the island with the Straw Hats,\NSanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I can't do that!\NEven if I could, what about Baratie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that after you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, we're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, you can't die.\NFor our mother's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a memory I can't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big fight between our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only a child
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was wondering why our sweet mother\Nwas that angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it became clear afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mother was pregnant at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was strongly against turning you four\Ninto cold killing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you serious?!\N--Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do such a terrible thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The surgery is prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! They're {\i1}my{\i0} children!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without emotions, they're not humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to be monsters.\NWinning wars is all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The re-establishment of the Vinsmoke Family\Nthat once conquered the North Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What it takes to accomplish \Nthat goal is strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give my children the ultimate strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you--? No! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey! Don't do it!\NThey're {\i1}my{\i0} kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then the surgery was performed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our mother later took a drug\Nto foil our father's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing, Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She took a powerful drug that could affect\Nthe manipulated Bloodline Elements.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But her desperate action was fruitless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They found superhuman-like abnormalities\Nin my brothers' body one after another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The surgery was a success.\N--Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry! Their genetic blueprints \Nwon't be affected by some drug.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.\NOnly Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right.\NLet's watch over his growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry? Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0} is feeding birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mustn't have that kind of attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept growing up as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, our mother \Ngot weaker and weaker due
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the after effects from the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she died because of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiju! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is your dad doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he does is train us\Nand he never plays with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just happy that Ichiji, Niji and Yonji\Nseem to be fine soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji cooked for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think Sanji told me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "Get well soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the greatest kid in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mother looked truly happy\Nfrom the bottom of her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji got beaten up by Ichiji \Nand the others again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to call someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Instead, Reiju,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can make it\Nuntil you kids are fully grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I now understand why she smiled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think she wasn't regretting\Nwhat happened to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or her own decision and everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such compassion to lay flowers for the dead\Nis useless in my own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But our father's beliefs were\Nthe total opposite of our mother's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he never accepted who you were.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He blamed you for everything that happened\Nand gave you a hard time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever cook again either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji is a worthless failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Failure! Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I don't wanna stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind!\NI'm scared! I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Help! They're gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get out of this kingdom!\NDon't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna stop you.\NYou can take the key to the iron mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can I ask just one last \Nfavor as your father, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever admit that I'm your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:22:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in front of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that I don't \Nwant anyone to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though our mother is no longer with us,\Nher grace is still there inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that you're a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mother protected her child \Nat the risk of her own life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was born with the spark of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child is you, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're kinder than everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Desperate, all-out attacks!\NBrook strikes a blow with everything he's got{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Pedro tries to carry out his mission -\Nboth of their fights come to a thrilling climax!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Luffy has broken out and\Nlaunches an attack on the Big Mom Pirates to save Sanji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"To Reach Sanji! Luffy's Vengeful Hell-bent Dash!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
